### Health
GET http://localhost:3000/api/health

### Mood - Read
GET http://localhost:3000/api/mood-entries

### Mood - Create
POST http://localhost:3000/api/mood-entries
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": "gut",
  "energy_level": 7,
  "stress_level": 4,
  "notes": "Eintrag aus REST Client",
  "latitude": 48.208174,
  "longitude": 16.373819,
  "weather_conditions": "bewoelkt",
  "activity": "lernen"
}

### Mood - Update (ID anpassen)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/mood-entries/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "mood": "neutral",
  "energy_level": 6,
  "stress_level": 5,
  "notes": "Update aus REST Client",
  "latitude": 48.208174,
  "longitude": 16.373819,
  "weather_conditions": "sonnig",
  "activity": "pause"
}

### Sensor - Read
GET http://localhost:3000/api/sensor-readings

### Sensor - Create
POST http://localhost:3000/api/sensor-readings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sensor_type": "gps",
  "data": {
    "latitude": 48.208174,
    "longitude": 16.373819
  }
}
